data.description: Welcome home to this FOUR bedroom, two bath split floor plan beauty that has been renovated with no expense spared. NEW flooring, paint, custom-built closets, windows, siding, and roof,. With the kitchen open to the breakfast area and spacious living room, inside entertaining with plenty of room is enjoyable. The wood-burning fireplace makes for a comfy, cozy setting for our few but welcomed cold days. This home as a separate formal dining area and utility room. Outside entertaining is perfect, like literally perfect! Landscaped yard, garden area and a very large covered patio / carport make outside BBQs and crawfish boils easy and fun. And let me not forget to mention the fire pit area which will keep the kiddos entertained with their smores-making events. The 12 x 20 double-lofted shed and covered lean to is lagniappe. Plenty of space to store tools, toys or both. This beautiful home and half acre sit in Flood Zone X which typically does not require flood insurance. Measurements are M/L. Make the call to your realtor today. You will not regret it.
